      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-auc-cmd-cod    to   w-acc-com-com          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A trattamento Return                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-150.
       acc-cmd-mnu-034.
