           perform   vis-pag-mir-000      thru vis-pag-mir-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a inizio accettazione               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-000.
       acc-cmd-mnu-035.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tasto Prnt                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
