      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      ".p"                 to   w-acc-com-com          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura tasto Return                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A trattamento Return                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-150.
       acc-cmd-mnu-040.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tasto Pf1                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Simulazione di impostazione di '.t', rubri- *
      *                  * ca telefonica                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      ".t"                 to   w-acc-com-com          .
