      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      ".u"                 to   w-acc-com-com          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura tasto Return                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A trattamento Return                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-150.
       acc-cmd-mnu-044.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tasto Pf4                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Simulazione di impostazione di '.a', cambio *
      *                  * azienda                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      ".a"                 to   w-acc-com-com          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura tasto Return                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A trattamento Return                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-150.
       acc-cmd-mnu-045.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tasto Select                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Simulazione di impostazione di '.r',        *
      *                  * programmi recenti                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      ".r"                 to   w-acc-com-com          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura tasto Return                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A trattamento Return                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-150.
       acc-cmd-mnu-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tasto Up                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
