           perform   lin-024-spc-000      thru lin-024-spc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Posizionamento su ultimo mark point         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-mnu-nmk        to   w-acc-com-i01          .
       acc-cmd-mnu-055.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo terminazione esecuzione in back-  *
      *                  * ground                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cnt-ter-bkg-000      thru cnt-ter-bkg-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Cursore supplementare                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-let-mnu-lmk
                    (w-acc-com-i01)       to   v-lin                  .
           move      04                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "====>"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice comando in Bold, se in modalita'     *
      *                  * grafica                                     *
