      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A reimpostazione in mark point          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cmd-mnu-055.
       acc-cmd-mnu-065.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tasto Down  o Return da mark point       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
