                            with no lock
                            at end
                            go to   dis-imp-stp-090.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Max su records di impegno stampanti         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        pss-tre              not  = "imp "
                     go to dis-imp-stp-090.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Record in area di lavoro                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      pss-dat              to   w-imp                  .
