           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Linea 24 a spaces                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   lin-024-spc-000      thru lin-024-spc-999        .
       blo-spo-sta-050.
