                                          to   w-fnd-auc-cmd-pos      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-hlp-scr-520.
       vis-hlp-scr-620.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
