      *                      * Verifica limite sinistro                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-auc-cmd-pos    =    w-fnd-auc-cmd-po1
                     go to vis-hlp-scr-520.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A sinistra                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-auc-cmd-po1    to   w-fnd-auc-cmd-pos      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-hlp-scr-520.
       vis-hlp-scr-640.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
