      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-auc-cmd-pos    =    w-fnd-auc-cmd-po2
                     go to vis-hlp-scr-520.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A sinistra                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-auc-cmd-po2    to   w-fnd-auc-cmd-pos      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-hlp-scr-520.
       vis-hlp-scr-660.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se 'Tab'                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
