      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-auc-cmd-li2    to   w-fnd-auc-cmd-lin      .
           move      w-fnd-auc-cmd-po2    to   w-fnd-auc-cmd-pos      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-hlp-scr-520.
