      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-hlp-scr-900.
       vis-hlp-scr-680.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
