      *              * Normalizzazione valori di accettazione          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-nxt-opn-nam          .
           move      zero                 to   w-nxt-opn-top          .
           move      zero                 to   w-nxt-opn-tpf          .
           move      spaces               to   w-nxt-opn-nmf          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio immagine video                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in Off                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
